message: /* Regulation and operation */  Adding information about mutual funds in India and ways to invest in mutual funds for Indians.
Added information that might help reducing confusion amongst people that come searching for the India based firm. Since both organisations have similar name, this information was deemed necessary.
The edit shows industry experts saying why one should invest in Raheja's Atharva and Vedaanta.
The edit includes the final outcome of the court case in Raheja Vedanta and Atharva
